undle.clearCache()`. Resetting the field seems sufficient, but if the locale changes, the cache could still return the previous locale. Having Locale.ROOT is fine, but should I clear it before each use? It looks like ResourceBundle caches by locale, so using clearCache might be the way to go. \n\nI'm also thinking about reflection to reset the messages bundle and whether to import Compatibility directly or use SWT publicly. Plus, I'm unsure about native image handling with private static fields. Responsibility for potential imports or checkstyle issues is on my mind as well.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03e72d197ecc5dca016a1e9ffeea84819793ddbd3fbf27abcb\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqHqAbAIzwHtuBswMBcBBLuce3sZFrRX_FxcQPKPOy9-pfrAW7LHVNiUIbG9wjSNLbZe-_E-9kjZJT_VKKVEZ488jAur7qN8vtCcg5ko-2b0QlOhoUUTVwpCKIJ3irVb5vpBMhy5kxqc7tF3-L-x6W7XAMeOcrjLjmqJtaTPgxBGdhdElshDhZyVTiws_KYMCzXieyeCfwQ5BHeh_EB28y6kYclE_ibBJHAliDHK2QFBpN5XYgL5Ssj8xgYVjHDDVeqCgmw2W1YxjhadLO0wy7e87KWV4-uP0U-d0coaFOS9GrUVESEERcG3y-xDmfdzQXpCQ2YaRSBBpjfx_ykEdTf1ggVbX06oDf9oaii7WjNgc7j5CW2O3AbCbGltKFqdJb6whXzIlhijV2CzOCfCNEs4AS-dXaijlxjQjUdmhgQ7h-H9SCZzqr4PTes0iWZwxUW0j_LrgVv0xFdS-NFmBpp1J9g-fD7cLcS3QHPH-YxmLN84TrM4j6PTALVVMMeNFct5DBZi02aghLmBJ8eoWN1syvEnwuB3ISLXeUPmlBbigP4DXehryNaS41CP38isSUoXTtcb0htzibgJOVqqxT3eZpYvl7fKYF51TXLSswt5ECxC0FhyGmcTFxYuDYTxaxwxOGbilSW3IIEb_11KwISFBWu0RcBdXtwESg-tDBuc_qLj6iQEfRR9cp_i1GgAybk-O7s9SnUiKKCUqDKB_TBMKQ7c2QXldJ0UgtMHqK6QG0PCm4QygzQhW3ZYgj_obVyHUj2QKAGUpstkk6Cb19qQ-EH4Cnj1fjyGDbJO9jAKbiE3wcusBmMh-8y_q1p1i3dfEGBOSnjr4SOJHSBTpwM-KAgw4J6Pp9HjM87t-7IXQFDjJ0Liiy8pBkntozeUGW_ReNS3YnewTkBdI7ktOpE_ydtTZ8U78fI_HxK20QOHv4oQkCX7Mf5JHm_ImkFispI8GwBCaL6L4DVGJOvvDNS3cFx0sMyESXs2TJ7GdPgu33nDU4VQkpgo6u5khwqSA5tuTO4DbX14LkQQmD1JmOgJ5Za-2VQXfn0LSNohOmhm13mGajIJCHmJmiyO4m43WTrljRnQ6gjiVBGND0nrsWqXknpPybgEE39DczmphzmjdmszDfmWXRsP_pWpYCTf02NECeDYkQATC7MOjs-J-2FHLzIWaIlaJKe9m3Z1MIQqPfwm69hW88S_lfHO1_RN5s3EXARuXo8-RLNYE2_urG2W7JipryaPip-8R9zIO9JCdfbkv2E1Kmeke1o